    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface ThrowingDoubleToShortFunction1
extends AbstractThrowingDoubleToShortFunction1<AbstractThrowingDoubleToShortFunction1.Handler>
    Represents a function that accepts a double-valued argument and produces a short-valued result or throws a throwable. This is the one-arity specialization of ThrowingToShortFunctionN. This is the double-consuming primitive specialization of ThrowingToShortFunction1. This is the short-producing primitive specialization of ThrowingDoubleFunction1. This is the throwing variation of DoubleToShortFunction1.

    This is a functional interface whose functional method is AbstractThrowingDoubleToShortFunction1.applyAsShort(double).

    Since:
    1.0.0
    See Also:
